  "description": "MAchine Translation Evaluation Online (MATEO) - A project that aims to facilitate machine translation (MT) evaluation by means of an easy-to-use interface that can evaluate given machine translations with a battery of automatic metrics. It caters to both experienced and novice users who are working with MT, such as MT system builders, and also researchers from Social Sciences and Humanities, and teachers and students of (machine) translation.",
